---
// ">_ Console" easter egg: a tiny fake shell. Commands are handled
// client-side (see src/scripts/console.ts) against build-time data.
---

<div class="term" id="term">
  <div class="term-out" id="term-out">visitor@pve-portfolio:~$ cat /etc/motd

  Bienvenue sur pve-portfolio.
  Ce terminal est un clin d'œil — mais il répond.
  Tapez `help` pour la liste des commandes.
</div>
  <div class="term-line">
    <span class="prompt" aria-hidden="true">visitor@pve-portfolio:~$</span>
    <input
      class="term-input"
      id="term-input"
      type="text"
      autocomplete="off"
      spellcheck="false"
      aria-label="Console interactive — tapez help pour la liste des commandes"
    />
  </div>
</div>
